Available Tools: get_weather_alerts | get_storm_warnings | get_air_quality_index
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "location": "string", "severity": "string" }
Response Schema: { "alerts": [{ "type": "string", "severity": "string", "message": "string", "expires": "string" }] }
---
Question: Are there any hurricane warnings currently active for Key West?
Call: { "func_call": "get_storm_warnings", "location": "Key West, FL", "severity": "extreme" }
Response: { "alerts": [{ "type": "Hurricane Warning", "severity": "extreme", "message": "Sustained winds of 120 mph expected within 36 hours. Evacuate immediately if in a low-lying zone.", "expires": "2024-06-15T10:00:00Z" }] }

Question: Check for heat advisories in Phoenix due to extreme temperatures.
Call: { "func_call": "get_weather_alerts", "location": "Phoenix, AZ", "severity": "high" }
Response: { "alerts": [{ "type": "Excessive Heat Warning", "severity": "high", "message": "Temperatures reaching 115°F expected. Drink plenty of fluids and stay in air-conditioned rooms.", "expires": "2024-06-16T20:00:00Z" }] }

Question: Is there a severe thunderstorm watch issued for Atlanta?
Call: { "func_call": "get_weather_alerts", "location": "Atlanta, GA", "severity": "severe" }
Response: { "alerts": [{ "type": "Severe Thunderstorm Watch", "severity": "severe", "message": "Large hail and damaging winds up to 70 mph are possible this afternoon.", "expires": "2024-06-15T19:00:00Z" }] }

Question: Get wind chill warnings for Anchorage regarding extreme cold.
Call: { "func_call": "get_storm_warnings", "location": "Anchorage, AK", "severity": "extreme" }
Response: { "alerts": [{ "type": "Wind Chill Warning", "severity": "extreme", "message": "Wind chills as low as -50°F will cause frostbite on exposed skin in minutes.", "expires": "2024-06-17T08:00:00Z" }] }

